Sentencas: The study on pure LNF cathode shows that the material sintered at 1100 degrees C exhibits optimal performance.
Titulo: Optimization of LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In order to improve the electrochemical performance, CGO powder is added to prepare the LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-delta-Ce0.9Gd0.1O2-alpha (LNF-CGO) composite cathode.
Titulo: Optimization of LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Electrochemical performance and characteristics of the LNF-CGO composite cathode, which is used for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells, are investigated.
Titulo: Optimization of LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Effect of the CGO content on the electrochemical performance of the composite cathode, especially the polarization resistance, is investigated.
Titulo: Optimization of LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The optimized specific area resistance is only 0.37 Omega cm(2) when the CGO content is 29.4vol.% (30 wt.%).
Titulo: Optimization of LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The resistance of Cr poisoning was also investigated during along term (200 h) measurement; the result indicated that the composite cathode also showed high resistance of Cr poisoning.
Titulo: Optimization of LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3-δ cathode for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
